sentence: get saturday fares from washington to toronto
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v2.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.day_name||'"', '"'||v3.fare_id||'"', '"'||v4.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.city_name||'"', '"'||v7.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v8.city_code||'"', '"'||v8.city_name||'"', '"'||v9.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.day_name||'"' FROM fare v0, fare_basis v1,
 days v2, flight_fare v3, flight v4, airport_service v5,
 city v6, airport_service v7, city v8, days v9 
WHERE (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v1.basis_days = ANY v2.days_code) 
AND (v2.day_name = 'SATURDAY'))) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v3.fare_id) 
AND ((v3.flight_id = ANY v4.flight_id) 
AND (((v4.from_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) 
AND (v6.city_name = 'WASHINGTON'))) 
AND (((v4.to_airport = ANY v7.airport_code) AND ((v7.city_code = ANY v8.city_code) 
AND (v8.city_name = 'TORONTO'))) 
AND ((v4.flight_days = ANY v9.days_code) AND (v9.day_name = 'SATURDAY')))))));
